Description:
Canonicalize a host name: return a name other hosts can understand, i.e.
usually the host name including FQDN.

Files:
lib/canon-host.c
lib/canon-host.h
m4/canon-host.m4

Depends-on:
getaddrinfo
strdup

configure.ac:
gl_PREREQ_CANON_HOST

Makefile.am:
lib_SOURCES += canon-host.c

Include:
"canon-host.h"

License:
LGPL

Maintainer:
Jim Meyering
